(530, 1, '2016-06-14 12:03:04', '2016-06-14 07:03:04', 'Adidas est le commanditaire officiel de la NBA, mais difficile de croire qu''ils puissent savoir d''avance qui gagnera la finale.\n\nIls annonçaient pourtant la vente de vêtements pour Golden State, champions 2016 de la NBA, hier sur leur application.\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en">So Adidas is pretty confident that the Warriors are gonna win tonight... <a href="https://t.co/vUeG4u0DkY">pic.twitter.com/vUeG4u0DkY</a></p>\n— RyanWalbolt (@RyanWalbolt72) <a href="https://twitter.com/RyanWalbolt72/status/742330807826649088">June 13, 2016</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\nD''accord, aucune équipe dans l''histoire n''est revenu de l''arrière 3-1, mais Lebron James se montre très motivé à créer ce précédant. Notons d''ailleurs que James est porte-parole pour Nike...\n\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-533" src="http://maniacdesports.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/lebronhype-300x227.jpg" alt="OAKLAND, CA - JUNE 07: LeBron James #23 of the Cleveland Cavaliers celebrates their 95 to 93 win over the Golden State Warriors in overtime during Game Two of the 2015 NBA Finals at ORACLE Arena on June 7, 2015 in Oakland, California. NOTE TO USER: User expressly acknowledges and agrees that, by downloading and or using this photograph, user is consenting to the terms and conditions of Getty Images License Agreement. (Photo by Ezra Shaw/Getty Images) ORG XMIT: 556889089 ORIG FILE ID: 476311456" width="600" height="453" />\n\nSource: <a href="http://www.foxsports.com/nba/story/adidas-golden-state-warriors-nba-championship-gear-before-game-5-cleveland-cavaliers-061316">Fox Sports</a>', 'Golden State déjà champions selon Adidas.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'golden-state-deja-champions-selon-adidas', '', '', '2016-06-14 12:03:04', '2016-06-14 07:03:04', '', 0, 'http://maniacdesports.com/?p=530', 0, 'post', '', 