(776, 1, '2016-06-22 17:40:36', '2016-06-22 21:40:36', '<p dir="ltr" lang="en">En réponse aux questions des journalistes sur le futur nom de l''équipe de Las Vegas dans la NHL, Bill Foley a simplement dit qu''il aimait le nom des Black Knights.</p>\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en">Il n''a cependant pas voulu confirmer que ce serait le nom choisit. Il avance qu''il y a encore plusieurs options possibles.</p>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en"><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/NHL?src=hash">#NHL</a> NEWS: Bill Foley loves the "Las Vegas Black Knights" but did not confirm the name. Many other options out there <a href="https://t.co/H87HXSvcTD">pic.twitter.com/H87HXSvcTD</a></p>\n— The Hockey Press® (@TheHockeyPress) <a href="https://twitter.com/TheHockeyPress/status/745723578549673984">June 22, 2016</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>', 'Les Black Knights de Las Vegas? Rien de confirmé.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'les-black-knights-de-las-vegas-rien-de-confirme', '', '', '2016-06-22 17:40:36', '2016-06-22 21:40:36', '', 0, 'http://maniacdesports.com/?p=776', 0, 'post', '', 0),
