(993, 1, '2016-06-29 17:05:46', '2016-06-29 21:05:46', '<p dir="ltr" lang="en">Angela Price, conjointe de Carey, ne semble pas trop déçue.</p>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en">Crazy hockey day...sure excited to welcome some of our kelowna friends to Montreal though 🤗<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/thatshockey?src=hash">#thatshockey</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/NHLTrade?src=hash">#NHLTrade</a></p>\n— Angela Price (@ByAngelaPrice) <a href="https://twitter.com/ByAngelaPrice/status/748257922631634944">June 29, 2016</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\nP.K. Subban: Le succès de l''équipe avant la qualité du spectacle. <a href="https://t.co/BIlwMOlQpz">pic.twitter.com/BIlwMOlQpz</a>\n\n— François Legault (@francoislegault) <a href="https://twitter.com/francoislegault/status/748252639230595072">June 29, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n<p dir="ltr" lang="fr">Les fans cherchent cependant un coupable.</p>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="fr">En fouillant un peu j''ai trouvé quelqu''un de content.... <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Ch?src=hash">#Ch</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/habs?src=hash">#habs</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/subban?src=hash">#subban</a><a href="https://t.co/9UlE6fIZ4O">pic.twitter.com/9UlE6fIZ4O</a></p>\n— Pascal Allard (@allardpascal) <a href="https://twitter.com/allardpascal/status/748253744043790336">June 29, 2016</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\nDans le fond , il n''y a que Max Pacioretty qui est bien content de ce trade la <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/subban?src=hash">#subban</a>\n\n— Martin Davidson (@Martiindavidson) <a href="https://twitter.com/Martiindavidson/status/748250222304821248">June 29, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en">Hopefully <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Habs?src=hash">#Habs</a> captain Max Pacioretty now shows up to play every game next season like P.K. Subban always did.</p>\n— Stu Cowan (@StuCowan1) <a href="https://twitter.com/StuCowan1/status/748255275719634944">June 29, 2016</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<a href="https://twitter.com/GMolsonCHC">@GMolsonCHC</a> pourquoi !!! Pourquoi !!!! Echange le coach avant subban do something you are loosing fan right now !!!!\n\n— Filou (@GalarneauF) <a href="https://twitter.com/GalarneauF/status/748256223976366080">June 29, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="fr">Encerclez le Jeudi 2 Mars sur votre Calendrier.\nSubban va recevoir une ovation monstre au Centre Bell.\n..Et il va se battre avec Pacioretty</p>\n— Anthony Désaulniers (@Anthodezo) <a href="https://twitter.com/Anthodezo/status/748253470931705857">June 29, 2016</a></blockquote>\nLa thématique du feu...\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\nLIVE LOOK AT MONTREAL RIGHT NOW. <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Subban?src=hash">#Subban</a> <a href="https://t.co/pu7UCK5aIu">pic.twitter.com/pu7UCK5aIu</a>\n\n— Tim and Sid (@timandsid) <a href="https://twitter.com/timandsid/status/748253000553086976">June 29, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en"><a href="https://twitter.com/CanadiensMTL">@CanadiensMTL</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/PKSubban1">@PKSubban1</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/GMolsonCHC">@GMolsonCHC</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/RDSca">@RDSca</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/TVASports">@TVASports</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/subbanforweber?src=hash">#subbanforweber</a> <a href="https://t.co/EED0pWyAfW">pic.twitter.com/EED0pWyAfW</a>\n\n— Bishop (@andre_bishop04) <a href="https://twitter.com/andre_bishop04/status/748270334713921536">June 29, 2016</a></blockquote>\nEt plus de frustration:\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\nCriss de calice de tabarnak d''osti de sacrament de trou de cul <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Habs?src=hash">#Habs</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Subban?src=hash">#Subban</a>\n\n— Chase Straight (@ChaseStraight) <a href="https://twitter.com/ChaseStraight/status/748249657835458562">June 29, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="und">NOOOOOOOOOOOOO <a href="https://twitter.com/PKSubban1">@PKSubban1</a> <a href="https://t.co/Tlfn9WzeZI">pic.twitter.com/Tlfn9WzeZI</a></p>\n— Marc-André Grondin (@MA_Grondin) <a href="https://twitter.com/MA_Grondin/status/748255952692985856">June 29, 2016</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\nSubban embraced the <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/canadiens?src=hash">#canadiens</a> history, the fans, donated $10 mill to local kids hospital, played street hockey with kids - and gets dealt.\n\n— Mike Zeisberger (@Zeisberger) <a href="https://twitter.com/Zeisberger/status/748250636530122753">June 29, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-partner="tweetdeck">\nIn a few years, Shea Weber''s contract will be a punch line just like Scott Gomez'' contract was a few years ago.\n\n— Simon Boisvert (@simonsnake70) <a href="https://twitter.com/simonsnake70/status/748260642746994693">June 29, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\nThe curse of St. Patrick rolls on... <a href="https://twitter.com/NHL">@NHL</a>\n\n— Coach (@CMPunk) <a href="https://twitter.com/CMPunk/status/748256264807841792">June 29, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>', 'Les réactions à l''échange de P.K. Subban.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'les-reactions-a-lechange-de-p-k-subban', '', '', '2016-06-29 17:05:46', '2016-06-29 21:05:46', '', 0, 'http://maniacdesports.com/?p=993', 0, 'post', '', 0),
