(1204, 1, '2016-07-07 00:03:28', '2016-07-07 04:03:28', 'Le UFC 200 est une carte phénoménale, mais le main event a toujours été le combat revanche entre Jon Jones, champion qui n''a jamais perdu sa ceinture, contre Daniel Cormier, champion par intérim.\n\nÀ un peu plus de 72 heures de l''événement, alors que Jon Jones a participé à des événements promotionels du UFC plus tôt aujourd''hui, Dana White a dû annoncer ce soir que Jones aurait testé positif à des tests de l''agence antidopage américaine.\n\nJones est donc retiré de l''événement et le main event devient Brock Lesnar vs Mark Hunt malgré que ce sera toujours un combat de 3 rounds.\n\nWhite aimerait conserver Daniel Cormier sur la carte, mais la nouvelle est une véritable bombe aussi peu de temps avant l''événement.\n\nIl faudra voir comment le UFC traitera le dossier avec le passé de Jon Jones.\n\n<img class="alignnone wp-image-1205 size-full" src="http://localhost/maniacdesports/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/JonJonesarrestado.jpg" alt="JonJonesarrestado" width="600" height="400" />\n\nSource: <a href="http://www.thescore.com/mma/news/1056077">The Score</a>', 'Jon Jones retiré du UFC 200.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jon-jones-retire-du-ufc-200', '', '', '2016-07-07 00:03:28', '2016-07-07 04:03:28', '', 0, 'http://maniacdesports.com/?p=1204', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(1205, 1, '2016-07-07 00:02:48', '2016-07-07 04:02:48', '', 'JonJonesarrestado', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jonjonesarrestado', '', '', '2016-07-07 00:02:48', '2016-07-07 04:02:48', '', 1204, 'http://localhost/maniacdesports/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/JonJonesarrestado.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(1206, 1, '2016-07-07 00:03:19', '2016-07-07 04:03:19', '', 'MMA: UFC 182-Jones vs Cormier', 'Jan 3, 2015; Las Vegas, NV, USA; Jon Jones (red gloves) celebrates after defeating Daniel Cormier (not pictured) in their light heavyweight title fight at UFC 182 at the MGM Grand Garden Arena. Jones won. Mandatory Credit: Jayne Kamin-Oncea-USA TODAY Sports', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mma-ufc-182-jones-vs-cormier', '', '', '2016-07-07 00:03:19', '2016-07-07 04:03:19', '', 1204, 'http://localhost/maniacdesports/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Jon-Jones.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(1209, 1, '2016-07-07 09:21:09', '2016-07-07 13:21:09', 'Très peu de pitié pour Jon Jones de la part des autres combattants du UFC suite à l''annonce qu''il a <a href="http://maniacdesports.com/2016/07/07/jon-jones-retire-du-ufc-200/">testé positif</a> à un test antidopage.\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en">Fucking cheaters u guys need drugs to fight? Fuck you all. 👈🏻 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/FuckTheCheaters?src=hash">#FuckTheCheaters</a> NO RESPECT 💯</p>\n— Manny Gamburyan (@MannyGamburyan) <a href="https://twitter.com/MannyGamburyan/status/750899020730540032">July 7, 2016</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\nAll the eyes are on you <a href="https://twitter.com/JonnyBones">@JonnyBones</a> ‼WTF Dude!!\n\n— Sean Spencer (@seanspencer170) <a href="https://twitter.com/seanspencer170/status/750899448964755456">July 7, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en">Can''t say I''m surprised. <a href="https://t.co/F2eVRTRXEb">https://t.co/F2eVRTRXEb</a></p>\n— Colby Covington (@ColbyCovMMA) <a href="https://twitter.com/ColbyCovMMA/status/750907304351043584">July 7, 2016</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<a href="https://twitter.com/JonnyBones">@JonnyBones</a> doesn''t wanna be saved don''t save em he don''t wanna be saved don''t save em. <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/UFC200?src=hash">#UFC200</a>\n\n— Jeremy Stephens (@LiLHeathenMMA) <a href="https://twitter.com/LiLHeathenMMA/status/750907383119884288">July 7, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en">Damn I thought I messed up my career with my bad decisions whole you know how much money this guy has wasted <a href="https://t.co/8hbCJhZ32M">https://t.co/8hbCJhZ32M</a></p>\n— Chris Leben (@ChrisLebenMMA) <a href="https://twitter.com/ChrisLebenMMA/status/750919588582461440">July 7, 2016</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\nUn point positif dans cette histoire, est la preuve que le UFC est sérieux concernant le dopage en annulant ainsi le combat principal du plus gros gala de son histoire. Ça nous fait comprendre le retour de GSP.\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\nDirty fighters better check under their beds because <a href="https://twitter.com/usantidoping">@usantidoping</a> gonna get you\n\n— Chris Camozzi (@ChrisCamozzi) <a href="https://twitter.com/ChrisCamozzi/status/750902886054268928">July 7, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\nPlusieurs sont cependant déçus ou surpris que le combat n''aie pas lieu ainsi. Nombreux compatissent aussi avec Daniel Cormier qui perd la chance d''unifier les titres.\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\nGreat day of training.. Looking forward to UFC 200.. Giving Twitter a looksies before bed one more ti.. OMFG\n\n— Josh Samman (@JoshSamman) <a href="https://twitter.com/JoshSamman/status/750900958855561216">July 7, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en"><a href="https://twitter.com/dc_mma">@dc_mma</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/ufc">@ufc</a>, I feel for ya. I know it feels to have your opponent get pulled 3 days before the fight due to being dishonorable. <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/norespect?src=hash">#norespect</a>\n\n— Dan Henderson (@danhendo) <a href="https://twitter.com/danhendo/status/750902731792003072">July 7, 2016</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\nHonestly, I''m crushed by this. Was really looking forward to this fight, after all that build up... <a href="https://t.co/M0yBzJqmXM">https://t.co/M0yBzJqmXM</a>\n\n— Aljamain Sterling (@FunkMaster_UFC) <a href="https://twitter.com/FunkMaster_UFC/status/750910326283964416">July 7, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">Shit was looking forward to that war ! <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/UFC200?src=hash">#UFC200</a>\n\n— Sergio Pettis (@sergiopettis) <a href="https://twitter.com/sergiopettis/status/750901960132399104">July 7, 2016</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\nFlying to Vegas and my jaw dropped once I got WiFi...\n Speechless is all I can say!\n\n— Anthony Johnson (@Anthony_Rumble) <a href="https://twitter.com/Anthony_Rumble/status/750908662130978816">July 7, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">Gotta feel real bad for DC right now. He had a lot to prove with Jones. Needs to get a fight and that PPV cut to make him feel better.\n\n— Chris Weidman (@ChrisWeidmanUFC) <a href="https://twitter.com/ChrisWeidmanUFC/status/750917444538077184">July 7, 2016</a></blockquote>\nFinalement, ils sont aussi plusieurs à s''offrir pour affronter Daniel Cormier sur la carte de samedi malgré les quelques heures qui nous séparent de l''événement.\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en">Hey <a href="https://twitter.com/danawhite">@danawhite</a> if you need someone, give me a shot</p>\n— Tom Lawlor (@FilthyTomLawlor) <a href="https://twitter.com/FilthyTomLawlor/status/750900307085799424">July 7, 2016</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\nBlack Panty Night! <a href="https://twitter.com/ufc">@UFC</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/danawhite">@Danawhite</a> give me <a href="https://twitter.com/dc_mma">@dc_mma</a> vs <a href="https://twitter.com/roynelsonmma">@roynelsonmma</a> + PPV. I am in after I beat the black beast... <a href="https://t.co/bQC4OZCwsB">https://t.co/bQC4OZCwsB</a>\n\n— Roy Nelson (@roynelsonmma) <a href="https://twitter.com/roynelsonmma/status/750901678103080960">July 7, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en">I was the last LHW Strikeforce Champion. I will be the next LHW <a href="https://twitter.com/ufc">@ufc</a> Champion if given this fight. <a href="https://twitter.com/danawhite">@danawhite</a></p>\n— Gegard Mousasi (@mousasi_mma) <a href="https://twitter.com/mousasi_mma/status/750911162603102208">July 7, 2016</a></blockquote>\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\nL''offre la plus intéressante semble cependant être venue du champion middleweight Michael Bisping qui dit qu''à 2 mois d''avis, 2 semaines ou 2 jours, il est prêt à se battre champion vs champion.\n\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n2 months, 2 weeks, 2 days...... Hmmm middle vs light heavy???? I stand by my words. I''d do it!\n\n— michael (@bisping) <a href="https://twitter.com/bisping/status/750920474884923397">July 7, 2016</a>\n</blockquote>\n\nSource: <a href="http://www.mmafighting.com/2016/7/7/12115190/pros-react-to-usada-pulling-jon-jones-from-ufc-200">mmafighting.com</a>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>', 'Jon Jones: Aucun respect des autres combattants.', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jon-jones-aucun-respect-des-autres-combattants', '', '', '2016-07-07 09:21:09', '2016-07-07 13:21:09', '', 0, 'http://maniacdesports.com/?p=1209', 0, 'post', '', 0),
