(1263, 1, '2016-07-10 08:20:53', '2016-07-10 12:20:53', 'Selon People Magazine, Derek Jeter se serait marié hier soir, avec sa conjointe la mannequin Hannah Davis.\n\nLa liste de conquêtes plus ou moins officielles de Jeter a longtemps fait jaser. Certains se sont donc amusés avec cette nouvelle:\n<blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-lang="en">\n<p dir="ltr" lang="en">People magazine says Derek Jeter &amp; swimsuit model Hannah Davis got married tonight. Had a tremendous dating career <a href="https://t.co/o1ClhUVAWs">pic.twitter.com/o1ClhUVAWs</a></p>\n— Darren Rovell (@darrenrovell) <a href="https://twitter.com/darrenrovell/status/751969185069137920">July 10, 2016</a></blockquote>\nFélicitations aux nouveaux mariés. Spécialement à Jeter?\n\n<img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-1265" src="http://localhost/maniacdesports/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/hannah-davis-2016-photo-sports-illustrated-x159793_tk5_01424-rawwmfinal1920.jpg" alt="hannah-davis-2016-photo-sports-illustrated-x159793_tk5_01424-rawwmfinal1920" width="1281" height="1920" />\n\n<script src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" async="" charset="utf-8"></script>', 'Derek Jeter enfin marié?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'derek-jeter-enfin-marie', '', '', '2016-07-10 08:20:53', '2016-07-10 12:20:53', '', 0, 'http://maniacdesports.com/?p=1263', 0, 'post', '', 0),
